text: Hallgarten is a surname. Hallgarten may also refer to: * Hallgarten (Pfalz), a municipality in Rhineland-Palatinate, Germany * Hallgarten (Rheingau), a Stadtteil of Oestrich-Winkel, Hesse, Germany * Hallgarten Prize, a design prize won by George Henry Bogert among others * Hallgarten Hall, a Dartmouth College building
title: Hallgarten (disambiguation)
